{"tid":1300354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與網民發起抵制行動有關？ 無綫突然取消商場活動","createTime":"2019-07-09T10:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T10:46:39.000Z","uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6f336666799bd0985825838fa1b33ab0aad53031","tid":1300354,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"今年香港中學文憑試（DSE）喺聽日放榜，放榜前好多應屆考生嘅心情都難免緊張，所以無綫原本喺今晚（放榜前夕）喺觀塘嘅一個商場舉行活動「DSE考生-放榜前的一個晚上」，仲安排咗唔少歌手同藝人幫考生打氣，例如有陳柏宇、麥明詩、馮盈盈及王灝兒（JW）等等。喺噚日，無綫突然喺Facebook專頁通知活動取消，至於原因就未有交代。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bzyEJrtLix5NEF2mY2udPw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-07/e99dcd40-a205-11e9-ad57-3d64543b0577\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FbzyEJrtLix5NEF2mY2udPw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-07%2Fe99dcd40-a205-11e9-ad57-3d64543b0577&h=fc5d4964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日唔少網民認為無綫新聞偏頗，除咗有人喺網上發起抵制行動之外，前日更有團體發起遊行（仍在申請不反對通知書），其中一站可能會途經無綫電視城。對於活動取消，唔少網民都紛紛留言問原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/09/I269FV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F09%2FI269FV.png&h=0472b878&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}